public CToolsTraceChannel createChannel(java.lang.String sReceiverName)

Create a Ctool Trace Channel instance. Ctool Trace Channel is used to configurate trace operation.

Parameters:

createTrigger

public CToolsTraceTrigger createTrigger(java.lang.String sSourceName)
                                 throws ScriptingException
Create a Ctool Trace Trigger interface. This interface is used to setup triger jobs for trace associated with the export.

Parameters:
sSourceName - name of the trace export source - CPU/STM etc. The name should be same as returned by DebugSession::getName().
